Class AdminController

java.lang.Object
com.example.oopproject.controllers.AdminController
@RestController @RequestMapping("/api/admin") public class AdminController extends Object
REST controller for admin-related operations on workouts and exercises. Provides endpoints to create, update, delete, and retrieve workouts and exercises.
